# vdl4k Project Structure and Goals

## Code Structure
```
vdl4k/
├── bin/
│   └── vdl4k          # Main executable
├── lib/
│   ├── utils.sh         # Core utilities
│   ├── validators.sh    # URL/input validation  
│   └── video_utils.sh   # Video processing
├── config/
│   └── default.conf     # Configuration template
└── doc/
    └── manual.md        # Documentation
```

## Project Goals
1. Modular architecture
2. Easy configuration
3. 4K video support
4. Batch processing
5. Comprehensive logging
